      "canon": "Yes",
      "notes": "Overview\r\nThe Academy of Broom Flying is a premier institution dedicated exclusively to the art of broom flight. Nestled in a wizarding community renowned for its aerial sports and efficient magical courier services, this school hones the skills that launch many graduates into professional broom sports teams or elite delivery roles. The curriculum is designed to provide mastery over every aspect of flightâfrom the enchanted maneuvers that keep riders aloft to the charm work that fineâtunes their broomsâwhile also equipping students with essential knowledge of muggle society and magical history.\r\n\r\nIntegrated Occult Traditions\r\nAt the Academy of Broom Flying, a tapestry of authentic magical traditions informs every lesson:\r\n\r\n\r\n \t\r\nRunes of the Wind:Rooted in ancient script-based rituals, this tradition celebrates the belief that properly inscribed runes can channel and regulate the gusts essential for flight. It underpins both the theoretical and practical aspects of broom maintenance and aerodynamics.\r\n\r\n \t\r\nCelestial Charmcraft:Drawing inspiration from historical practices of invoking protective enchantments on transport, this tradition infuses charm work with techniques traditionally used to safeguard and accelerate magical travel. Its influence is evident in every incantation that empowers a broomâs performance.\r\n\r\n \t\r\nBroomcraft Heritage:Centered on centuriesâold practices passed down from legendary broommakers and aerial tacticians, this tradition emphasizes both the artistry and engineering behind broom design. It enlivens the study of History at the academy, linking past breakthroughs to modern advancements.\r\n\r\n \t\r\nVeiled Integration:Recognizing that many broom flyers become professionals in muggle-dominated arenas, this tradition teaches discreet and effective interaction with nonâmagical society. It guides the âMugglesâ course, ensuring that every graduate can navigate the muggle world while preserving wizarding secrecy.\r\n\r\n\r\nTogether, these traditions form a cohesive foundation that interweaves practical flight instruction, charm refinement, historical perspective, and cultural savvy throughout every aspect of the academyâs curriculum.\r\n\r\nArchitecture\r\nThe Academyâs campus is modern and functional. Its facilities consist of well-appointed classrooms and training arenas designed around expansive open spaces that allow for both indoor and outdoor flight practice. In keeping with its singular focus, stateâofâtheâart flight simulators, broom repair workshops, and aerodynamically optimized training grounds are seamlessly integrated into the building design, embodying a sleek, utilitarian aesthetic that prioritizes performance and safety.\r\n\r\nAreas Served\r\nThe academy attracts students from across the wizarding world, with many applicants coming from regions with strong traditions in broom sports. Its reputation for producing elite flyers and innovative couriers appeals to families and communities that value a blend of athletic prowess, technical skill, and magical scholarship.",
      "notes-value": "<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"55\" data-end=\"67\">Overview</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"660\">The Academy of Broom Flying is a premier institution dedicated exclusively to the art of broom flight. Nestled in a wizarding community renowned for its aerial sports and efficient magical courier services, this school hones the skills that launch many graduates into professional broom sports teams or elite delivery roles. The curriculum is designed to provide mastery over every aspect of flightâfrom the enchanted maneuvers that keep riders aloft to the charm work that fineâtunes their broomsâwhile also equipping students with essential knowledge of muggle society and magical history.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"699\">Integrated Occult Traditions</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"701\" data-end=\"797\">At the Academy of Broom Flying, a tapestry of authentic magical traditions informs every lesson:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-start=\"799\" data-end=\"2048\">\r\n \t<li class=\"\" data-start=\"799\" data-end=\"1086\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"801\" data-end=\"1086\"><strong data-start=\"801\" data-end=\"823\">Runes of the Wind:</strong><br data-start=\"823\" data-end=\"826\" />Rooted in ancient script-based rituals, this tradition celebrates the belief that properly inscribed runes can channel and regulate the gusts essential for flight. It underpins both the theoretical and practical aspects of broom maintenance and aerodynamics.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1411\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1411\"><strong data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1115\">Celestial Charmcraft:</strong><br data-start=\"1115\" data-end=\"1118\" />Drawing inspiration from historical practices of invoking protective enchantments on transport, this tradition infuses charm work with techniques traditionally used to safeguard and accelerate magical travel. Its influence is evident in every incantation that empowers a broomâs performance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1413\" data-end=\"1722\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1415\" data-end=\"1722\"><strong data-start=\"1415\" data-end=\"1439\">Broomcraft Heritage:</strong><br data-start=\"1439\" data-end=\"1442\" />Centered on centuriesâold practices passed down from legendary broommakers and aerial tacticians, this tradition emphasizes both the artistry and engineering behind broom design. It enlivens the study of History at the academy, linking past breakthroughs to modern advancements.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1724\" data-end=\"2048\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"2048\"><strong data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"1749\">Veiled Integration:</strong><br data-start=\"1749\" data-end=\"1752\" />Recognizing that many broom flyers become professionals in muggle-dominated arenas, this tradition teaches discreet and effective interaction with nonâmagical society. It guides the âMugglesâ course, ensuring that every graduate can navigate the muggle world while preserving wizarding secrecy.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2050\" data-end=\"2264\">Together, these traditions form a cohesive foundation that interweaves practical flight instruction, charm refinement, historical perspective, and cultural savvy throughout every aspect of the academyâs curriculum.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2271\" data-end=\"2287\">Architecture</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2778\">The Academyâs campus is modern and functional. Its facilities consist of well-appointed classrooms and training arenas designed around expansive open spaces that allow for both indoor and outdoor flight practice. In keeping with its singular focus, stateâofâtheâart flight simulators, broom repair workshops, and aerodynamically optimized training grounds are seamlessly integrated into the building design, embodying a sleek, utilitarian aesthetic that prioritizes performance and safety.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2785\" data-end=\"2801\">Areas Served</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2803\" data-end=\"3130\">The academy attracts students from across the wizarding world, with many applicants coming from regions with strong traditions in broom sports. Its reputation for producing elite flyers and innovative couriers appeals to families and communities that value a blend of athletic prowess, technical skill, and magical scholarship.</p>",
